se itself. Small finds, sculpture and inscriptions predominate. The museum collection continues upstairs with non-archaeological material (and a single inscription). The courtyard of the building holds a large collection of architectural pieces and inscriptions",{"settlement":75,"region":116,"country":117,"address":118,"geo":119},"Palermo","Italy","Via Marco Tullio Cicerone, 90018 - Termini Imerese (PA)",{"lat":120,"lon":121},37.98655109,13.69587845,{"_":123,"mainLang":124,"languages":125},"Latin","la",[123],{"type":127,"bibl":128},"edition",[129,139,149,165,20],{"author":130,"date":86,"citedRange":131,"ptr":132,"ref":134,"inscriptionDate":86,"title":136,"citation":137,"uri":138},"Romano","187-188",{"target":133},"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/LXIPEQLG",{"_":135,"target":135},"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003145","Inscriptio Thermis nuper inventa","\u003Cspan>Baldassare Romano, «Inscriptio Thermis nuper inventa», \u003Ci>Effemeridi Scientifiche e Letterarie per la Sicilia\u003C/i> 1, fasc. 4 (1832): 187–88\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/LXIPEQLG",{"author":130,"date":140,"citedRange":141,"ptr":142,"ref":144,"inscriptionDate":140,"title":146,"citation":147,"uri":148},"1838","99 no.16",{"target":143},"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/25ZN5T5X",{"_":145,"target":145},"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001618","Antichità termitane","\u003Cspan>Baldassare Romano, \u003Ci>Antichità termitane\u003C/i> (Palermo: Tipografia di Francesco Lao, 1838)\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/25ZN5T5X",{"type":150,"n":151,"author":152,"date":153,"citedRange":154,"ptr":158,"ref":160,"inscriptionDate":153,"title":162,"citation":163,"uri":164},"corpus","CIL","Mommsen","1883",{"ref":155},{"_":156,"target":157},"7406","http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883",{"target":159},"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI",{"_":161,"target":161},"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589"